import Vue from 'vue'
import Vuex from 'vuex'
import mutations from './mutations'
import actions from './actions'
import getters from './getters'

Vue.use(Vuex)

const state = {
  transcriptionsData: [],
  errorMessage: ''
}

export default {
  namespaced: true,
  state,
  mutations,
  actions,
  getters
}
